    "content": "\n\n\n\n## **정맥점적 주입시 인라인필터를 사용하는 주사제** \n\n약제팀 2026.02.10. \n\n- ※ 인라인필터는 국내 허가사항에 인라인필터 사용이 명시되어 있는 주사제와 TPN(Total Parenteral Nutrition) 제제를 투여하는 경우 급여가 인정된다. \n\n## **국내 허가사항에 인라인필터 사용이 명시되어 있는 주사제** \n\n|분류|약품코드|약품명|성분명|**인라인필터 규격**|**비고**||\n|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|\n|항암제|XAVLMAB|Bavencio 200mg|Avelumab|**0.2㎛ 저단백결합**<br>**(PES권장)**|||\n|항암제|XBLINA3|Blincyto 35mcg|Blinatumomab|**0.2㎛ 저단백결합**|||\n|항암제|XRAMUC1|Cyramza 100mg|Ramucirumab|**0.22㎛ 이하**<br>**저단백결합**|||\n|항암제|XRAMUC5|Cyramza 500mg|Ramucirumab||||\n|항암제|XDARAT1|Darzalex 100mg|Daratumumab|**0.22㎛ 이하**<br>**저단백결합**<br>**(PES/PVDF)**|||\n|항암제|XDARAT4|Darzalex 400mg|Daratumumab||||\n|항암제|XTRZDER|Enhertu 100mg|trastuzumab deruxtecan|**0.2 ~ 0.22㎛**<br>**저단백결합**|**전용필터**||\n|항암제|XDURVAL1|Imfinzi 120mg|Durvalumab|**0.2 ~ 0.22㎛**<br>**저단백결합**|||\n|항암제|XDURVAL5|Imfinzi 500mg|Durvalumab||||\n|항암제|XDTLMAB|Jemperli 500mg|Dostarlimab|**0.2㎛ 저단백결합**|||\n|항암제|XCABAZT6|Jevtana 60mg|Cabazitaxel|**0.22㎛ 이하**<br>**저단백결합**|||\n|항암제|XTRZEM1|Kadcyla 100mg|trastuzumab emtansine|**0.2 ~ 0.22㎛**<br>**저단백결합**|||\n|항암제|XTRZEM16|Kadcyla 160mg|trastuzumab emtansine||||\n|항암제|XPEMB1|Keytruda 100mg|Pembrolizumab|**0.2 ~ 0.22㎛**<br>**저단백결합**|||\n|항암제|XNIVOL1|Opdivo 100mg|Nivolumab|**0.2 ~ 0.22㎛**<br>**저단백결합**|||\n|항암제|XNIVOL2|Opdivo 20mg|Nivolumab||||\n|항암제|XPTAX100|Padexol 100mg|Paclitaxel|**0.22㎛ 이하**<br>**(PVC-free 호환)**|||\n|항암제|XPTAX300|Padexol 300mg|Paclitaxel||||\n|항암제|XSILTU1Y|Sylvant 100mg|Siltuximab|**0.2㎛ 저단백결합**|||\n|항암제|XPTAX30W|Taxol 30mg|Paclitaxel|**0.22㎛ 이하**<br>**(PVC-free 호환)**|||\n|항암제|XATEZOL|Tecentriq 1200mg|Atezolizumab|**0.2 ~ 0.22㎛**<br>**저단백결합**|||\n|항암제|XTISLE1|Tevimbra 100mg|Tislelizumab|**0.2 ~ 0.22㎛**<br>**저단백결합**|||\n|항암제|XTEMSI|Torisel 30mg|Temsirolimus|**0.2 ~ 0.22㎛**<br>**저단백결합 (PES)**|||\n|항암제|XIPIL5|Yervoy 50mg|Ipilimumab|**0.2 ~ 0.22㎛**<br>**저단백결합**|||\n|항암제|XAFLIB1|Zaltrap 100mg|Aflibercept|**0.2㎛ 저단백결합**|||\n|항암제|XAFLIB2|Zaltrap 200mg|Aflibercept||||\n|항생제|XAMBIS50W|Ambisome 50mg|Liposomal AmB|**제공된 5㎛**<br>**시린지필터 사용**|**권장**||\n|항생제|XISAVU|Cresemba 200mg|Isavuconazole|**0.2 ~ 1.2㎛**<br>**저단백결합 (PES)**|||\n|일반|XRESLIZ|Cinqair 100mg|Reslizumab|**0.2㎛ 저단백결합**|||\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n|일반|XABCIX|Clotinab 10mg|Abciximab|**0.2 ~ 0.22㎛**<br>**저단백결합**||\n|---|---|---|---|---|---|\n|일반|XIDURS|Hunterase 6mg|Idursulfase beta|**0.2㎛ 저단백결합**||\n|일반|XAVALGLU|Nexviazyme 100mg|Avalglucosidase alfa|**0.2㎛ 저단백결합**||\n|일반|XOCRELZ|Ocrevus 300mg|Ocrelizumab|**0.2 ~ 0.22㎛**<br>**저단백결합**||\n|일반|XABATA250|Orencia 250mg|Abatacept|**0.2 ~ 1.2㎛**<br>**저단백결합**||\n|일반|XINFLX100|remiCADE 100mg|Infliximab|**1.2㎛ 이하**<br>**저단백결합 (PES)**||\n|일반|XINFLI100|remSIMA 100mg|Infliximab|||\n|일반|XGODAL5IV|SIMPONI IV 50mg|Golimumab|**0.22㎛ 이하**<br>**저단백결합**||\n|일반|XUSTEK1|STELARA IV 130mg|Ustekinumab|**0.2㎛ 저단백결합**||\n|일반|XATIG25|Thymoglobulin 25mg|Antithymocyte<br>immunoglobulin|**제공된 0.22㎛**<br>**시린지필터 사용**|**권장**|\n\n\n\n## **TPN(Total Parenteral Nutrition)제제-완제품** \n\n|TPN(3 in 1)|XNTENS5|XNTENS5|Ntense EF 506mL inj|Ntense EF 506mL inj|glusose+amino acids<br>+lipid|glusose+amino acids<br>+lipid|**1.2㎛**|**1.2㎛**|**권장**|\n|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|\n|TPN(3 in 1)|XFOMSC9||FOMS TNA 986ml central  inj||glusose+amino acids<br>+lipid+eletrolytes||**1.2㎛**||**권장**|\n|TPN(3 in 1)|XOMAP9P||Omapone peri 952ml||glusose+amino acids<br>+lipid+eletrolytes||**1.2㎛**||**권장**|\n|TPN(3 in 1)|XOMAP14||Omapeone Peri 1448ml inj||glusose+amino acids<br>+lipid+eletrolytes||**1.2㎛**||**권장**|\n|TPN(3 in 1)|XOMAP72||Omapone peri 724ml inj||glusose+amino acids<br>+lipid+eletrolytes||**1.2㎛**||**권장**|\n|TPN(3 in 1)|XSMOFKC14||SmofKabiven CENTRAL 1477ml||glusose+amino acids<br>+lipid+eletrolytes||**1.2㎛**||**권장**|\n|TPN(3 in 1)|XSMOFKP19||SmofKabiven PERI 1904ml||glusose+amino acids<br>+lipid+eletrolytes||**1.2㎛**||**권장**|\n|TPN(3 in 1)|XSMOFKP12||SmofKabiven PERI 1206ml||glusose+amino acids<br>+lipid+eletrolytes||**1.2㎛**||**권장**|\n|TPN(2 in 1)|XKABITP1||Kabitwin peri NO1 1000ml inj||glusose+amino acids<br>+eletrolytes||**0.2㎛**||**권장**|\n|**원내 사용가능한 인라인필터**||||||||||\n|**물품코드**||**물품명**||**규격**||**보험수가**||**특징**||\n|05034480104373||IV IN LINE FILTER**(0.2㎛), AEF1E**,<br>[PALL]||**0.2㎛**, AEF1E, 50EA/B||4,490||저단백결합(low protein<br>binding)필터||\n|05034480310354||IV IN LINE FILTER**(1.2㎛),**<br>**TNA2E(NLF2E)**, [PALL]||**1.2㎛**, NLF2E, 50EA/B||4,490||**저단백결합 필터 아님,**<br>**암비솜, 비쥬다인, 토리셀,**<br>**TPN투여시 사용가능**||\n|05034480001412||I.V. FILTER**(0.2㎛), NEO96E**[PALL]||**0.2㎛**, NEO96, 50EA/B||8,260||**주로 신생아에서 사용,**<br>**endotoxin까지 제거가능**||\n|2001000520343||INFU-GREEN PLUS,**1.2㎛**Filter,<br>[MEDI LINE]||**1.2㎛**Filter, 120ea/B||4,490||저단백결합(low protein<br>binding)필터||\n|2001000520367||Extension Set(**1.2㎛**Filter+3way)<br>INFU-GREEN PLUS[MEDI LINE]||**1.2㎛ **Filter, 100ea/box||4,490||저단백결합(low protein<br>binding)필터||\n|2001000561254||NATURE (F),**0.2μm/25cm**, [MEDI<br>LINE ACTIVE KOREA]||**0.2μm**/25cm||4,490||저단백결합(low protein<br>binding)필터||\n|2005201600019||OLEFUSION 수액세트, 전규격, [DRB<br>HEALTHCARE]||**0.2㎛**||9,230||Enhertu전용,<br>저단백결합(low protein<br>binding)필터 일체형||\n\n\n\n"
